resume: Ami Shubhash Bolchi is the story Netaji Subhas Chandra Bose  who comes into the life of struggling Debabrata  and through him, Netaji helps to awaken the Bengalis from "Sleep" and acts as a super hero. This movie is the Bengali version of Manjrekars earlier original Marathi film along the same lines called Me Shivajiraje Bhosale Boltoy.
